Package: kcmsurvey
Title: Make using survey data easier
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Claire", "Evans", , "clevans@kingcounty.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package hosts a suite of functions that make it easier to use survey data. You can easily transform data from wide to long, rename those transformed columns, create estimates and confidence intervals, as well as work with data visualization. 
